Package gov.sandia.geotessbuilder

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    BuilderUtils
    A collection of static methods that operate on GeoTessModels to modify their structure in various ways.
    Edge
    Edge represents the edge of a triangle.
    GeoTessBuilderMain
    Class provides a main() method to implement construction of a new GeoTessGrid or resolution refinement of an existing GeoTessModel based on a specified Properties file.
    GridBuilder  
    InitialSolid  
    PolygonGB
    Wrapper around Polygon that implements methods to work with Vertex objects instead of unit vectors.
    RefineModel
    Class to that implements resolution refinement of another GeoTessModel
    Tessellation
    Tessellation manages a single instance of multi-level tessellation of a unit sphere.
    TessellationPrimary  
    TessellationRefined  
    Triangle
    Triangle is essentially an array of 3 Vertex objects which define a spherical triangle on the surface of a unit sphere.
    Vertex
    Vertex represents a single point on the surface of a unit sphere, represented by a unit vector.
